      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk. it's just that everyone says \"it gets better\" or \"time heals,\" but it doesn't feel like that. it feels like the floor just fell out from under me. how am i supposed to just go through the motions for the next 40 years when the only thing that made sense is gone? it feels like i'm just being forced to exist in a world that doesn't even have my person in it anymore. it's exhausting.",
