    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that there's no \"processing\" it. it's not a wound that's gonna scab over, it's just... total annihilation. i look at the morning and it's just more of this same heavy, suffocating weight. it feels like i'm just being punished by staying alive. if everything that made life worth living is dead, why am i still expected to keep performing the role of a person?",
